liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: No late changes at the Gabba tonight. Brisbane have opted against naming Jack Payne, who was in a week-long race against time to prove his fitness. The Lions in the end decided it wasn't worth risking his ankle, and have picked Darcy Gardiner instead. Carlton have mixed things up this week, boosted by the returns of some star forwards. Harry McKay, Jack Martin, Oliver Hollands and Jordan Boyd are all in to the 22, with Brodie Kemp, David Cunningham, Matt Owies and Matt Kennedy out. Subs are Jarryd Lyons for Brisbane and Matt Kennedy for Carlton.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: The final teams and subs are in

children.content: No late changes at the Gabba tonight.

Brisbane have opted against naming Jack Payne, who was in a week-long race against time to prove his fitness. The Lions in the end decided it wasn't worth risking his ankle, and have picked Darcy Gardiner instead.
Carlton have mixed things up this week, boosted by the returns of some star forwards.
Harry McKay, Jack Martin, Oliver Hollands and Jordan Boyd are all in to the 22, with Brodie Kemp, David Cunningham, Matt Owies and Matt Kennedy out.
Subs are Jarryd Lyons for Brisbane and Matt Kennedy for Carlton.
